					Using Icons, Images, and Exit Buttons.
					
Icons :
root = Tk()
root.iconbitmap('Address of icon')

Exit Button :
button_quit = Button(root, text="Exit Program", command = root.quit)

Images  We need to install some library to put image on the windows:
libraries are :- PIL (Python Imaging Library) containing various modules like ImageTK, Image, ImageColor.
from PIL import ImageTk, Image 
# pip install Pillow to install the Pillow library

my_image = ImageTk.PhotoImage(Image.open("Address of the Image."))
my_label = Label(image=my_image)
my_label.pack()


